reviews.content: I did my company Picklenall after party here. The service was incredible and the seafood selection was so fresh. They have live seafood tank out front to pick from. We also had Karaoke that was set up by Mansger That, he made sure all our needs were met! Can’t wait to host my next party here at NPL!
Great place to throw birthday parties or events.  My friends and I loved the privacy and delicious array of foods. Service is top notch too! Will be coming here more often
Good for hanging out with buddies here. Also suitable for formal meetings. Good food and attentive server.
The restaurant has an elegant space, suitable for meetings and events, and offers fast and enthusiastic service.
Private dining place with airy space for family, and organizing parties is really ok Clean, enthusiastic and dedicated service, so wonderful
Luxurious restaurant, spacious space, beautifully decorated. - Enthusiastic support staff, friendly service. - Fresh, delicious ingredients. …
